You have to be a monk or a nun

16
00:02:19,705 --> 00:02:22,288
become a tera or a teri for 10 years.

17
00:02:23,129 --> 00:02:32,745
After 20 years, you're called a maha tera or a maha teri, which is a big tera, a big elder in one way or the other.

18
00:02:33,665 --> 00:02:40,616
Now, these days, you don't normally use the word maha tera except people who become quite elderly.

19
