interesting thing about a terror is that they can ordain but it's not you you don't do it that way usually you belong to an order a sect within uh the buddhist monastic community and somebody is ahead of that and that's that's the person who would ordain and so that way you know it is said you can um trace your lineage all the way back to the buddha

20
00:03:09,655 --> 00:03:22,776
At that time, Theramagir was attending upon the Buddha, and on one occasion, on his return from Antram, the Theram noticed a pleasant and beautiful mango grove, which he thought was an ideal spot for meditation.

21
00:03:23,957 --> 00:03:26,221
So he asked the Buddha's permission to let him go there.

22
00:03:26,921 --> 00:03:33,132
But as the Buddha was alone at the time, he was told to wait for a while until the arrival of some of the bhikkhus.

23
00:03:34,056 --> 00:03:42,568
The Tera was in a hurry to go, and so he repeated his request again and again until finally the Buddha told him to do as he wished.

24
00:03:43,991 --> 00:03:49,679
Thus Tera Megiya set out for the mango grove, sat at the foot of a tree and practiced meditation.

25
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:54,866
He stayed there the whole day, but his mind kept wandering and he made no progress.

26
00:03:55,848 --> 00:04:03,337
He returned in the evening and reported to the Buddha how all the time he was assailed with thoughts associated with the senses,

27
00:04:03,604 --> 00:04:30,608
with ill will and with cruelty so the Buddha told him that as a mind oops I've lost my sorry about that so the Buddha told him that as the mind is easily excitable and fickle one should control one's mind so if we go back to the verses

28
00:04:31,903 --> 00:04:39,314
Now in the first verse, there's nothing particularly important about the Pali as such, the words.

29
00:04:40,596 --> 00:04:54,257
So it's a case of the mind is excitable, unsteady, wavering, it's difficult to control, keep hold of, it's difficult to restrain, but yet one has to work at it as a fletcher straightens a bow.

30
00:04:54,757 --> 00:04:59,225
Now I did go onto YouTube and I found out how to straighten an arrow.

31
00:04:59,324 --> 00:05:00,526
Sorry, not a bow, an arrow.

